-- Formosa Plastic Raises Salaries by 3% From July, Economic Daily News Says
-- Weiyi Lim
-- 2010-07-14T22:31:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/formosa-plastic-raises-salaries-by-3-from-july-economic-daily-news-says.html

          
          
             Formosa Plastics Corp. raised 
salaries for all staff by three percent from July and every 
employee received an additional bonus of NT$10,000 cash, the 
Economic Daily News reported, citing an unidentified official 
at the Ministry of Economic Affairs. China Steel Corp. may also
increase wages by three percent, according to the Taipei-based 
Chinese-language daily.  
